import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useParams, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const CBOdetailsPage = () => { const { id } = useParams(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const [cbo, setCBO] = useState(null); const [error, setError] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { const fetchCBO = async () => { try { const response = await fetch(`/api/cbos/${id}`); if (!response.ok) throw new Error("Failed to fetch CBO"); const json = await response.json(); if (cbo && cbo.files) { // ‚úÖ Ensure `cbo` and `cbo.files` exist before logging console.log("üîπ CBO Data:", cbo); console.log("üîπ CBO Files:", cbo.files); } setCBO(json); } catch (error) { console.error("‚ùå Error fetching CBO:", error.message); setError(error.message); } }; fetchCBO(); }, [id]); if (error) return
